🚀 Calling all TikTok Shop Owners! 🚀 

Introducing the The No.1 TikTok Shop Affiliate Outreach Bot App 🛍️ TTinit 🛍️

* Desktop App: Automates TikTok Seller Center messaging and invitations, compatible with Windows and MAC. ⭐️
* Creator Database: Identifies and messages 25k creators using filters or direct targeting from the dashboard. 🎯
* Multiple Accounts: Streamlines managing multiple brands or shops from one app. 💻
* User Interface: Offers a sleek and intuitive interface for easy navigation. ✨
* Follow-up Messaging: Automatically sends follow-up messages to re-engage creators. 👋
* Personalized Outreach: Enhances messages with the creator's name for increased engagement. 💌
* Regional Support: Targets creators in the UK, US, and Europe. 🌍
* Discreet Operation: Safely mimics human behavior to prevent detection of TT algo. 🕵️‍♂️
* Community Invitation: Join the Discord community to boost your TikTok Shop. 🚀

🆓 Try our app for Free : Signup for free via our website at https://www.ttinit.com
💬 Join our Discord server for support and inquiries
